column2: SELECT photoobj.obj, photoobj.psfmag_u, photoobj.psfmag_g, photoobj.psfmag_r, photoobj.psfmag_i, photoobj.psfmag_z, photoobj.ra as photoobj_ra, photoobj.dec as photoobj_dec, star.apstar_id, star.ra as star_ra, star.dec as star_dec, aspcap.teff, aspcap.m_h, aspcap.logg, obj.j, obj.k, obj.ak_targ, photoobj.extinction_u, photoobj.extinction_g, photoobj.extinction_r, photoobj.extinction_i, photoobj.extinction_z, photoobj.psfmagerr_u, photoobj.psfmagerr_g, photoobj.psfmagerr_r, photoobj.psfmagerr_i, photoobj.psfmagerr_z into mydb.SDSSugrizTest from apogeeStar AS star CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (star.ra, star.dec, #) AS near JOIN photoobj ON near.objid = photoobj.objid JOIN aspcapStar as aspcap ON star.apstar_id = aspcap.apstar_id WHERE star.apstar_id = #M2#+##
